                Payment description must include:<br>
                Your registered email and phone number
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flow">
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-badge">1</div>
                <div>
                    <h3>Make Payment</h3>
                    <p>Transfer funds to our žiro account using your <b>registered</b> email and phone number in the payment description.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-badge">2</div>
                <div>
                    <h3>Capture Receipt</h3>
                    <p>Take a clear photo or scan of the payment confirmation. Ensure all details are visible.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-badge">3</div>
                <div>
                    <h3>Email Submission</h3>
                    <p>Send the receipt to <strong>tokens@yourapp.com</strong>. Tokens arrive within 24-48 hours.</p>
                </div>
